  "detailed_description": "Defender of the Kingdom: Tower Defense is a colorful medieval tower defense strategy game where orcs and their horde attacked the kingdom and now the fate of the kingdom is in your hands, defenders!<br><br>Murderous war began... Defense of the Kingdom – your primary goal. The people believe in you. Build a defensive line with a powerful tower and defend your kingdom. Build tower, upgrade your towers, use the magic support and stopped the invaders!<br><br>If you like tower defense then you will love Defender of the Kingdom!<br><br>Remember, defender – orcs must die! Are you ready? Let's start the battle!<br><br>Game Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Genre – strategy & tower defense<br></li><li> Amazing 3D graphics and heroic music<br></li><li> 40 interesting levels<br></li><li> 10 different towers with upgrades to increase strategic choice<br></li><li> Colorful magic support to eliminate enemies in defense zone</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Defender of the Kingdom: Tower Defense is a colorful medieval tower defense strategy game where orcs and their horde attacked the kingdom and now the fate of the kingdom is in your hands, defenders!<br><br>Murderous war began... Defense of the Kingdom – your primary goal. The people believe in you. Build a defensive line with a powerful tower and defend your kingdom. Build tower, upgrade your towers, use the magic support and stopped the invaders!<br><br>If you like tower defense then you will love Defender of the Kingdom!<br><br>Remember, defender – orcs must die! Are you ready? Let's start the battle!<br><br>Game Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Genre – strategy & tower defense<br></li><li> Amazing 3D graphics and heroic music<br></li><li> 40 interesting levels<br></li><li> 10 different towers with upgrades to increase strategic choice<br></li><li> Colorful magic support to eliminate enemies in defense zone</li></ul>",
